minor.comment: Normalize import of builtin modules to use the `node:` protocol.
Add a feature for injecting custom localized values into a compilation via the `getCustomDataPlaceholderForValueFunction` function on an instance of the `LocalizationPlugin`.
Support passing the `ignoreString` option to all loaders.

patch.comment: Fix a bug where `chunk.localizedFiles` was not set in incremental rebuilds.

minor.comment: Leverage webpack caching layer for localized and nonlocalized asset generation. Reduce unnecessary work.

patch.comment: Fix circular references between localized assets' "related" properties. This caused emitting of the webpack stats object to fail.
Improve performance of localized asset reconstruction.

minor.comment: Include webpack compilation in localizationStats callback.

patch.comment: Include CHANGELOG.md in published releases again
Include missing `type` modifiers on type-only exports.

minor.comment: Perform localization before devtool runs instead of after. This is more expensive but ensures source maps are correct.
Export a `TrueHashPlugin` that performs what the `realContentHash` option does, but without validating the localization plugin's options.

patch.comment: Add support for the `output.hashSalt` option when the `realContentHashes` feature is enabled.

minor.comment: Include an option called `realContentHash` that updates "[contenthash]" hashes to the actual hashes of chunks.
Add a warning if `optimization.realContentHash` is set.
Introduce a `formatLocaleForFilename` option to customize how a locale (or the lack thereof) is rendered in file paths.

patch.comment: Fix line endings in published package.
Update type-only imports to include the type modifier.
Change the peer dependency selector on `@types/node` to a wildcard (`*`).

minor.comment: Move the @types/node dependency to an optional peerDependency.
Convert LocalizationPlugin._stringKeys to public stringKeys property.

patch.comment: Ensure localization file path resolution can handle a UNIX file system on a Windows host, as is used by the unit tests.

minor.comment: Initial publish of webpack 5 compatible localization plugin.
